        "content": "**Axis Independence:** Time of flight $T$ depends only on $v_{0y}$, not $v_{0x}$.\n\n$$T = \\frac{2\\,v_{0y}}{g}$$\n\nHorizontal speed changes *where* the ball lands, never *when*."
